// Name: WaybillManager
// Desc: Creates and manages the Waybill window in Driver.
//
//  Messages posted by this system:
//  [ Major           | Minor               | Source        | Destination     ]
//  [ WaybillManager    WaybillsWindowShown   WaybillManager  WaybillManager  ]
//  [ WaybillManager    WaybillsWindowHidden  WaybillManager  WaybillManager  ]
